{"tid":1302891,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"應該加油  抵制  中聯辦的  書店....","createTime":"2019-07-10T06:02:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-11T01:07:13.000Z","uid":266121,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"6a338ee6e7419fe40695c59777d4bed7b7b5ae21","tid":1302891,"uid":266121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T06:02:10.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">港台節目《鏗鏘集》調查發現，商務印書館、三聯書店、中華書局等合共53間書店同隸屬聯合出版集團，當中的背後大股東正為中聯辦。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E6%94%BF%E6%83%85/193449/%E4%B8%AD%E8%81%AF%E8%BE%A6%E6%8E%A7%E5%88%B6%E6%9C%AC%E6%B8%AF%E9%81%8E%E5%8D%8A%E6%9B%B8%E5%BA%97-%E6%9E%97%E9%84%AD-%E5%8F%AA%E8%A6%81%E4%BE%9D%E6%B3%95%E4%B8%8D%E6%87%89%E5%B9%B2%E9%A0%90\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E6%2594%25BF%25E6%2583%2585%2F193449%2F%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E8%2581%25AF%25E8%25BE%25A6%25E6%258E%25A7%25E5%2588%25B6%25E6%259C%25AC%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E9%2581%258E%25E5%258D%258A%25E6%259B%25B8%25E5%25BA%2597-%25E6%259E%2597%25E9%2584%25AD-%25E5%258F%25AA%25E8%25A6%2581%25E4%25BE%259D%25E6%25B3%2595%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%2587%2589%25E5%25B9%25B2%25E9%25A0%2590&d=QYAfZ%2BMwCyPDsUhWB4j8CiNFMfcMnrnh95DLK%2BYL5kQ%3D&h=08da95ac\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E6%94%BF%E6%83%85/193449/%E4%B8%AD%E8%81%AF%E8%BE%A6%E6%8E%A7%E5%88%B6%E6%9C%AC%E6%B8%AF%E9%81%8E%E5%8D%8A%E6%9B%B8%E5%BA%97-%E6%9E%97%E9%84%AD-%E5%8F%AA%E8%A6%81%E4%BE%9D%E6%B3%95%E4%B8%8D%E6%87%89%E5%B9%B2%E9%A0%90</a>"},{"pid":"8d35dee34a04560a7c6f65b864afe585d01bda2f","tid":1302891,"uid":166117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T06:08:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2F50VqF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2F50VqF.png&h=67339252&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/R9VDG5G.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FR9VDG5G.png&h=e0e59300&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a02e48c68fa00101207dc23b8842b8c71ddddd4e","tid":1302891,"uid":66811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T01:07:13.000Z","msg":"中聯辦經營香港超過半數書店（都屬大品牌、各區有旺鋪或地鋪），行內人謂，一般書籍大約有七至八成在三中商書店售出，雖不致於壟斷香港書市，但市場份額極大，影響力強。近年，內地敏感「禁書」已於三中商絕迹，一些批評政府、有關社運傘運的書籍，亦不容易在三中商找到。中聯辦作為一個「聯絡」機構，直接插手書市，應被詰問，要解釋；中聯辦有能力透過市場銷售渠道的優勢，影響訊息流通，這是廣大市民應該關注的事。<br />\n<br />\n全文<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.mobi.yahoo.com/news/%E8%AB%8B%E8%AA%8D%E6%B8%85-%E4%B8%89%E4%B8%AD%E5%95%86-%E6%9B%B8%E5%BA%97%E7%9A%84%E5%B9%95%E5%BE%8C%E8%80%81%E9%97%86-%E4%B8%AD%E8%81%AF%E8%BE%A6-054449187.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.mobi.yahoo.com%2Fnews%2F%25E8%25AB%258B%25E8%25AA%258D%25E6%25B8%2585-%25E4%25B8%2589%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%2595%2586-%25E6%259B%25B8%25E5%25BA%2597%25E7%259A%2584%25E5%25B9%2595%25E5%25BE%258C%25E8%2580%2581%25E9%2597%2586-%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E8%2581%25AF%25E8%25BE%25A6-054449187.html&d=QYAfZ%2BMwCyPDsUhWB4j8CiNFMfcMnrnh95DLK%2BYL5kQ%3D&h=e302940e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.mobi.yahoo.com/news/%E8%AB%8B%E8%AA%8D%E6%B8%85-%E4%B8%89%E4%B8%AD%E5%95%86-%E6%9B%B8%E5%BA%97%E7%9A%84%E5%B9%95%E5%BE%8C%E8%80%81%E9%97%86-%E4%B8%AD%E8%81%AF%E8%BE%A6-054449187.html</a>"}]}